    <p>A X</p>
    <p>A  X X  A</p>
    <p>User Hist u1 u2 u3 u4 u5</p>
    <p>P[ X | A ] = 1/3</p>
    <p>P[ X | A with no X preceding ] = 1/2</p>
    <p>P[X |AX] 7</p>
